# Rust build artifacts
**/target

# Rustfmt backup files
**/*.rs.bk

# MSVC Windows debug info
*.pdb

# IDEs
.idea/
.vs/

# Generated dev-certs
cert/

# Example workspaces resolve their own lock files locally. The workspace-root
# Cargo.lock is committed for reproducible CI builds, but example lock files are
# not tracked.
examples/**/Cargo.lock
